+# Content Hub canonical write-path (P2B): runbook
+
+╨Ф╨░╤В╨░: 2026-03-07  
+╨в╨Ч: [TECH-SPEC-CURSOR-P2B-VK-IMPORTER-v1.md](TECH-SPEC-CURSOR-P2B-VK-IMPORTER-v1.md)
+
+╨Ч╨░╨┐╨╕╤Б╤М ╨▓ `content_hub.publication` ╨╕ `content_hub.link_map` ╨▓╤Л╨┐╨╛╨╗╨╜╤П╨╡╤В╤Б╤П **╤В╨╛╨╗╤М╨║╨╛ ╤З╨╡╤А╨╡╨╖** `content_hub_client` (╨╕╨╜╤Д╤А╨░-╤Б╨╗╨╛╨╣ ContentBackbone). ╨Т VK_Importer ╨╜╨╡╤В ╨┐╤А╤П╨╝╨╛╨│╨╛ SQL ╨╕ ╨╗╨╛╨║╨░╨╗╤М╨╜╨╛╨│╨╛ DAO ╨┤╨╗╤П canonical write.
+
+---
+
+## 1. ╨Ч╨░╨▓╨╕╤Б╨╕╨╝╨╛╤Б╤В╤М content_hub_client
+
+╨Ш╤Б╤В╨╛╤З╨╜╨╕╨║: `D:\Work\ContentBackbone\content_hub_client\`.
+
+**╨б╨┐╨╛╤Б╨╛╨▒ ╨┐╨╛╨┤╨║╨╗╤О╤З╨╡╨╜╨╕╤П:** ╨┤╨╛╨▒╨░╨▓╨╕╤В╤М ╨║╨╛╤А╨╡╨╜╤М ContentBackbone ╨▓ `PYTHONPATH`, ╤З╤В╨╛╨▒╤Л ╨╕╨╝╨┐╨╛╤А╤В `content_hub_client` ╨╜╨░╤Е╨╛╨┤╨╕╨╗ ╨╝╨╛╨┤╤Г╨╗╨╕.
+
+╨Я╤А╨╕╨╝╨╡╤А (PowerShell, ╤Б╨╡╤Б╤Б╨╕╤П):
+```powershell
+$env:PYTHONPATH = "D:\Work\ContentBackbone;$env:PYTHONPATH"
+python main.py upload-one 123
+```
+
+╨Ш╨╗╨╕ ╨▓ ╨╛╨┤╨╜╨╛╨╣ ╨║╨╛╨╝╨░╨╜╨┤╨╡:
+```powershell
+$env:CONTENT_HUB_WRITE_ENABLED="1"; $env:PYTHONPATH="D:\Work\ContentBackbone"; python main.py upload-one 123
+```
+
+╨С╨╡╨╖ `content_hub_client` ╨▓ PYTHONPATH ╨┐╤А╨╕ `CONTENT_HUB_WRITE_ENABLED=1` ╨▓ ╨╗╨╛╨│ ╨┐╨╕╤И╨╡╤В╤Б╤П ╨┐╤А╨╡╨┤╤Г╨┐╤А╨╡╨╢╨┤╨╡╨╜╨╕╨╡ ╨╕ ╨╖╨░╨┐╨╕╤Б╤М ╨╜╨╡ ╨▓╤Л╨┐╨╛╨╗╨╜╤П╨╡╤В╤Б╤П.
+
