+| `CONTENT_HUB_WRITE_DRY_RUN` | `0` | `1` тАФ dry-run: ╨║╨╗╨╕╨╡╨╜╤В ╨╜╨╡ ╨║╨╛╨╝╨╝╨╕╤В╨╕╤В ╨▓ ╨С╨Ф. |
+| `CONTENT_HUB_WRITE_STRICT` | `0` | `1` тАФ ╤Б╨▒╨╛╨╣ canonical write ╤Б╤З╨╕╤В╨░╤В╤М ╤Д╨░╤В╨░╨╗╤М╨╜╨╛╨╣ ╨╛╤И╨╕╨▒╨║╨╛╨╣ ╤И╨░╨│╨░. |
+| `CONTENT_HUB_PG_DSN` | тАФ | DSN PostgreSQL, ╨╜╨░╨┐╤А╨╕╨╝╨╡╤А `postgresql://user:pass@host:5432/Learn`. |
