+
+---
+
+## 3. ╨Т╨║╨╗╤О╤З╨╡╨╜╨╕╨╡ write-path
+
+1. ╨г╨▒╨╡╨┤╨╕╤В╤М╤Б╤П, ╤З╤В╨╛ ╨▓ ╨╛╨║╤А╤Г╨╢╨╡╨╜╨╕╨╕ ╨┤╨╛╤Б╤В╤Г╨┐╨╡╨╜ `content_hub_client` (PYTHONPATH = ╨║╨╛╤А╨╡╨╜╤М ContentBackbone).
+2. ╨Ч╨░╨┤╨░╤В╤М `CONTENT_HUB_WRITE_ENABLED=1` ╨╕ `CONTENT_HUB_PG_DSN=...` (╨╕╨╗╨╕ ╤Б╨╛╤Б╤В╨░╨▓╨╜╤Л╨╡ PG-╨┐╨╡╤А╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╨╜╤Л╨╡).
+3. ╨Ч╨░╨┐╤Г╤Б╨║╨░╤В╤М ╨┐╤Г╨▒╨╗╨╕╨║╨░╤Ж╨╕╤О ╨║╨░╨║ ╨╛╨▒╤Л╤З╨╜╨╛: `upload-one`, ╨┐╨░╨╣╨┐╨╗╨░╨╣╨╜ ╨╕ ╤В.╨┤. ╨Я╨╛╤Б╨╗╨╡ ╨║╨░╨╢╨┤╨╛╨│╨╛ publish ╨▓╤Л╨╖╤Л╨▓╨░╨╡╤В╤Б╤П ╨║╨╗╨╕╨╡╨╜╤В (upsert publication + link_map).
+
+---
+
+## 4. Dry-run
+
+`CONTENT_HUB_WRITE_DRY_RUN=1` тАФ ╨║╨╗╨╕╨╡╨╜╤В ╨╜╨╡ ╨▓╤Л╨┐╨╛╨╗╨╜╤П╨╡╤В commit; ╨▓ ╨╗╨╛╨│╨░╤Е ╤Д╨╕╨║╤Б╨╕╤А╤Г╨╡╤В╤Б╤П ╨╛╨┐╨╡╤А╨░╤Ж╨╕╤П (dry_run). ╨Ф╨░╨╜╨╜╤Л╨╡ ╨▓ ╨С╨Ф ╨╜╨╡ ╨╝╨╡╨╜╤П╤О╤В╤Б╤П.
