+---
+
+## 5. ╨Ю╤В╨║╨░╤В
+
+1. `CONTENT_HUB_WRITE_ENABLED=0` (╨╕╨╗╨╕ ╤Г╨┤╨░╨╗╨╕╤В╤М ╨┐╨╡╤А╨╡╨╝╨╡╨╜╨╜╤Г╤О).
+2. ╨Я╤Г╨▒╨╗╨╕╨║╨░╤Ж╨╕╤П ╨▓ VK ╨╕ `videos.db` ╤А╨░╨▒╨╛╤В╨░╤О╤В ╨║╨░╨║ ╤А╨░╨╜╤М╤И╨╡; canonical write ╨╜╨╡ ╨▓╤Л╨╖╤Л╨▓╨░╨╡╤В╤Б╤П.
+
+╨Я╤А╨╕ ╨┐╨╛╨╗╨╜╨╛╨╝ ╨╛╤В╨║╨░╤В╨╡ ╨║╨╛╨┤╨░: `git revert <commit>`, ╨╖╨░╤В╨╡╨╝ smoke-╨┐╤А╨╛╨▓╨╡╤А╨║╨░ publish-flow.
