+
+## 6. ╨Ь╨░╨┐╨┐╨╕╨╜╨│ (PublicationResult тЖТ client payload)
+
+- **global_uid / source_global_uid:** `vk_importer:video_record:<id>` ╨╕╨╗╨╕ `vk_importer:path:<normalized_file_path>`.
+- **destination:** `vk`.
