+- **status:** `published` | `failed`; **error:** `result.error_code` ╨┐╤А╨╕ ╨╛╤И╨╕╨▒╨║╨╡.
+- **published_at:** UTC ISO-8601 ╨┐╤А╨╕ ╤Г╤Б╨┐╨╡╤Е╨╡.
+
